dcterms:description: The dataset consists of pan-sharpened orthorectified Azersky (SPOT-7) images (red, green, blue, and near infrared channels) with 1.5-meter resolution and annotation masks, collected from 15 regions in Azerbaijan where the greenhouses are densely congested. The images cover a cumulative area of 1008 km2 and annotation masks contain 47559 polygons in total.
dcterms:title: Azersky (SPOT-7) images
